---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../../components/elements/Card.astro';
import Spacer from '../../components/elements/Spacer.astro';
---
<Layout 
  pageTitle="Now"
  description="An about page can only tell you so much about a person. To see what I'm involved with and engrossed in right now, check out my Now page."
>

	<p class="intro">An about page can only tell you so much about a person. To see what I'm involved with and engrossed in right now, check out my Now page (inspired by Derek Silver's <a href="https://nownownow.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener,noreferrer">nownownow.com</a> project).</p>
	<h2>Reading</h2>
	<p>Continuing my pace of reading mostly non-fiction whenever I have a little bit of free time. A friend lent me his copy of 'Salt: A world history' over the holiday break as a bit of a joke and I'm determined to work my way through it.</p>
	<ul class="cards">
		<li class="d_press-down">
				<Card
					cardType="media"
					layoutClass="column"
					cardClass="media"
					category="book"
					href="https://amzn.to/4vBCKtQ"
					imageUrl="https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Publication221/v4/e4/aa/68/e4aa6801-565b-5fb0-b8d2-e3b1f7de3d23/9780525558941.d.jpg/600x600bb.jpg"
					title="How to Change Your Mind"
					subtitle="Michael Pollan"
					timestamp="2019"
        />
		</li>
		<li class="d_press-down">
			<Card
				cardType="media"
				layoutClass="column"
				cardClass="media"
				category="book"
				href="https://amzn.to/4fmN3Me"
				imageUrl="https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Publication123/v4/b8/40/37/b84037f8-3371-9f68-d423-73b0b322e767/9781250123817.jpg/600x600bb.jpg"
				title="Factfulness"
				subtitle="Hans Rosling"
				timestamp="2020"
			/>
		</li>
		<li class="d_press-down">
			<Card
				cardType="media"
				layoutClass="column"
				cardClass="media"
				category="book"
				href="https://amzn.to/4wf6wpE"
				imageUrl="https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Publication124/v4/79/c6/04/79c604a3-10a1-4da4-2871-a4d8bbe01765/9780698139152.d.jpg/600x600bb.jpg"
				title="Salt: A world history"
				subtitle="Mark Kurlansky"
				timestamp="2020"
			/>
		</li>
	</ul>

	<Spacer size="md" />

	<h2>Listening to</h2>
	<p>Rediscovered an old Underworld record that I'd never dug into much beyond one or two songs. Good for a rainy day or a drive. Also getting served a lot of 'barber beats' mixes in my Youtube feed and they actually make for some decent background music while doing work.</p>
